# Before regenerating the start script with `setupTermuxArch re[fresh]`, first copy this file to another name such as `fbinds.prs`.  Then add as many proot statements as you want; The init script will parse file `fbinds.prs` at refresh adding these proot options to `startarch`.  The space before the last double quote is necessary.  Examples are included for convenience:
##############################################################################
# PRoot bind usage: PROOTSTMNT+="-b host_path:guest_path " # the space before the last double quote is necessary
